title: Getting Ghosted by Shaq | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 28
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


THE BABES talk EMBARRASSING text messages. Chris lack of music knowledge....he doesn't know the BEATles. Shout out to @tedmunzmosaicart for our new AMAZING studio sign! Going to movie or show premieres and parties are BRUTES! What is movie premiere etiquette? Chris finally gets his paws on some No Presh Pack peanut butter from Saratoga Peanut Butter. IT'S LIT. What's the best bread? Being at gun point sounds scary. The human body is SCARY! The babes break down how many youtube channels have over 100k subscribers. The babes get esoteric. SHOUT OUT TOM BRADY! Sal talks about the time him and the Impractical Jokers got ghosted by Shaquille O'Neal. Sal talks about how hard he worked as a kid to have his own phone line. Chris talks about how when he was a teenager his mother dated a close friend's father....NIGHTMARE! HEY BABE!


Rate us on iTunes!
